      <scopecontent id="aspace_253346027a941bff167e152f060f1e81">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection comprises material related to the work of Helen Haywood, illustrator of children's books. The material includes drawings, mock-ups, and typed stories.</p>
